What:		/sys/devices/platform/gvdu/interface/grant
Date:		October 2024
Contact:	Kanstantsin Yarmash <kyarmash@google.com>
Description:
		(WO) Writing this file with the base64 encoded grant string
		returned by the VDU server will store it as part of a directive
		that will be used in the authentication process.

What:		/sys/devices/platform/gvdu/interface/delegate
Date:		October 2024
Contact:	Kanstantsin Yarmash <kyarmash@google.com>
Description:
		(WO) Writing this file with the base64 encoded delegate string
		returned by the VDU server will store it as part of a directive
		that will be used in the authentication process.

What:		/sys/devices/platform/gvdu/interface/auth
Date:		October 2024
Contact:	Kanstantsin Yarmash <kyarmash@google.com>
Description:
		(WO) Writing this file with arbitrary content will trigger VDU HW
		authentication and will complete the session setup. The previously
		saved combination of grant and delegate will be used as the auth
		token required for this process. If the signature is inconsistent
		with the auth token this operation will return an error indicating
		that the VDU session setup failed.

